  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a wok over medium-high heat.",
    "Add minced garlic and stir-fry for about 30 seconds.",
    "Add chicken pieces, water chestnuts, bean sprouts, and pistachio nuts. Stir-fry for another minute.",
